.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-5::.
City: venice, san-francisco
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, romance
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, rock
There are 2 different nationalities: british, russian
2 different pets are kept: lizard, rat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, volleyball
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, tulip
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the russian##1
2. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsbellflower is the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the british is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
6. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| City           | san-francisco    | venice  |
| Movie-Genre   | romance       | mystery    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel        | rock       |
| Nationality   | russian       | british    |
| Pet           | rat           | lizard     |
| Sport         | skateboarding | volleyball |
| Flower     | tulip    | bellflower        |

